are directed somewhere else.

313
00:21:44,260 --> 00:21:46,340
Chief Advisor Rossiu...

314
00:21:47,380 --> 00:21:49,800
Someone must be made
to take responsibility.

315
00:21:49,930 --> 00:21:52,310
That is how a government functions.

316
00:22:00,190 --> 00:22:01,980
The Anti-Spiral...

317
00:22:02,730 --> 00:22:05,150
Who in the world
are they?

318
00:22:08,280 --> 00:22:09,820
Nia...

319
00:22:18,750 --> 00:22:21,170
What's all the ruckus, Rossiu?

320
00:22:23,380 --> 00:22:25,340
Rossiu?

321
00:22:25,840 --> 00:22:31,050
Supreme Commander Simon.
I hereby place you under arrest.

